commits.message:
build folder, apply theme & state management

>> error in import provider

Keep selections when they have non-empty sublayers

Rather than obltierating them in taht case as if they're empty, since
that precludes spawning a selection by drawing on it with a brush in
indirect mode.

Implement Drawpile 2.2 compatibility mode

Unlike the 2.1 compatibility mode, this is implemented at the
serialization and deserialization level. There's still some places where
it has to send different messages due to changing the compression
algorithm or something. This also rejigs the way MyPaint brush flags
work a bit, since that wasn't thought through correctly.
